subject: Hockey, Ice
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: In a tight-checking, physical game the patient Spartans prevailed by scoring three goals in the final 10 minutes 7 seconds before a Frozen Four-record crowd of 19,432 at the Scottrade Center.
